SQM4 Linux Yocto Project BSP
============================

This layer extends functionality of the meta-fsl-bsp-release layer (https://source.codeaurora.org/external/imx/meta-fsl-bsp-release), which it depends on.

The following SQM4 boards are supported in this release:

   * ELNICO SQM4-UL6-EasyBoard (sqm4ul6-eb)


Quick Start Guide
-----------------

Install repo first, if not done yet:
$ mkdir ~/bin
$ curl http://commondatastorage.googleapis.com/git-repo-downloads/repo  > ~/bin/repo
$ chmod a+x ~/bin/repo
$ PATH=${PATH}:~/bin

Fetch all the layers:
$ mkdir <release>    # e.g. eln-release-bsp-sumo
$ cd <release>
$ repo init -u https://github.com/elnicoCZ/eln-release-bsp-manifest.git -b imx-linux-sumo
$ repo sync

Setup build directory:
$ [MACHINE=<machine>] [DISTRO=fsl-imx-<backend>] source ./eln-setup-release.sh -b <build folder>
e.g.
$ MACHINE=sqm4ul6-eb DISTRO=fsl-imx-xwayland source ./eln-setup-release.sh -b build-sqm4ul6-eb-xwayland
